  "format": "The first movie auction. After mourning the ArcLight's closure and a rules primer from Danny Heifetz, Sean, Amanda, and Chris each get $1,000 to buy five upcoming 2021 films. Bobby Wagner keeps the books.",
  "segments": [
    {
      "kind": "auction",
      "heading": "The paddles",
      "saleLabel": "Inaugural sale · 2021",
      "slates": [
